suite /swiːt/

(suites) 

1. N-COUNT A suite is a set of rooms in a hotel or other building. 套房 

例： They had a fabulous time during their week in a suite at the Paris Hilton. 他们在巴黎希尔顿酒店的套房里度过了非常愉快的一周。 

2. N-COUNT A suite is a set of matching furniture. 一套家具 

例： ...a three-piece suite. …一组三件套家具。 

3. N-COUNT A bathroom suite is a matching bathtub, sink, and toilet. (浴室) 套件 

例： ...the horrible pink suite in the bathroom. …浴室里那组难看的粉红色套件。

